body_html:
The original issue was missing android artifacts from jcenter, leading to compile failures like
Failed to resolve: org.tensorflow:tensorflow-android:+

This issue was fixed over Sunday/Monday (Oct 15th/16th 2017) and at this point all tensorflow-android aar versions should accessible from jcenter again.

body:
The original issue was missing android artifacts from jcenter, leading to compile failures like
 `Failed to resolve: org.tensorflow:tensorflow-android:+`

This issue was fixed over Sunday/Monday (Oct 15th/16th 2017) and at this point all tensorflow-android aar versions should accessible from jcenter again.
